192
00:21:34,430 --> 00:21:43,098
And instead of getting really uptight about that and wanting to strangle them, you can use it as a meditational object.

193
00:21:43,159 --> 00:21:47,644
The beginning, the rising and the falling, you see, so it's all impermanent.

194
00:21:49,108 --> 00:21:53,515
And of course, both ways in regards to oneself and in regards to the other.

195
00:21:54,476 --> 00:21:58,201
So that brings us to the end of the section on breathing.

